      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">It takes more than pretty photos and a clever URL to make a successful blog. The following 50 bloggers set themselves apart by encouraging reader interaction and changing the health and wellness space for the better.</div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2013-11-11"
>
  November 11, 2013  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
    <a
    href="http://greatist.com/p/sophia-breene"
    title="User profile of "
