          </div>
          <h1 class="title" id="page-title" itemprop="name headline alternativeHeadline">50 Bloggers Making a Difference in Fitness, Health, and Happiness</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="top-share">
          <div class="group_share" data-recirc-section>
